{"tid":1660642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自動繳費工具 PPS HK Pay Bot","createTime":"2019-10-17T15:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T19:40:12.000Z","uid":261374,"like":100,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b897b68bffbd2e8ed9e9d1c6c8eb3522c8b62a","tid":1660642,"uid":261374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"早排睇到呢個post: <br />\n<blockquote>【公民抗命】教你如何合法交稅/差餉/水費交到政府蝕錢 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是用左幾日時間，寫左個Google Chrome既extension用黎交下帳單咁<br />\nURL: <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pps-hk-pay-bot/mlpilfangidnjfmahodhihmmaenpidgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fpps-hk-pay-bot%2Fmlpilfangidnjfmahodhihmmaenpidgk&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=e810a1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pps-hk-pay-bot/mlpilfangidnjfmahodhihmmaenpidgk</a><br />\n<br />\nSource Code: <a href=\"https://github.com/freehk-developer/chrome-ppshk-pay-bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ffreehk-developer%2Fchrome-ppshk-pay-bot&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=1469c161\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/freehk-developer/chrome-ppshk-pay-bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果擔心安全問題，你可以搵身邊信得過既IT朋友睇下source code，確定無問題先再manual install黎用既，Github Readme度有教點manual install<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用法好簡單，你首先登入左PPS HK先，然後就按個extension既icon，會有個popup彈出黎，填好張form按執行就得喇<br />\nP.S. 第一次就淨係set行一次，試左無問題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baaZmAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaaZmAX.png&h=d42021a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果發現有咩bug既，歡迎係Github或者經Google Form話我知，Google Form條link係Github Readme度<br />\n<br />\n另外我都見到有人寫左個PPS Automator (<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/ppsautomator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fppsautomator&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=db9e237f\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/ppsautomator</a>)，咁其實佢只係公開左開頭少少關於UI(用戶介面)既code，想自己build都無得build，安唔安全就大家自行判斷啦"},{"pid":"4324f927e66a044179e2fdcda7b916da3d743621","tid":1660642,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"601842301cd9bfda5cdeb4395f597e655b6b7db9","tid":1660642,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:01:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"313f57398fa21340cd4433e6d57a60c05b5aea90","tid":1660642,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:04:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0e848dd1f9502c266e30ad946ea6a1143d9acf","tid":1660642,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"行動post要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6203e40fbb69768c2fa0f0727c6d185b86bdc6","tid":1660642,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9xH6TZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9xH6TZ.jpg&h=1e2b265c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f8940284daa7a993b3c1472bacff3a20e4bd668","tid":1660642,"uid":40493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T00:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4d23330bc26d6bd615df389ce6157fa1e23d07","tid":1660642,"uid