t%2Fmlpilfangidnjfmahodhihmmaenpidgk&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=e810a1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pps-hk-pay-bot/mlpilfangidnjfmahodhihmmaenpidgk</a><br />\n<br />\nSource Code: <a href=\"https://github.com/freehk-developer/chrome-ppshk-pay-bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ffreehk-developer%2Fchrome-ppshk-pay-bot&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=1469c161\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/freehk-developer/chrome-ppshk-pay-bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果擔心安全問題，你可以搵身邊信得過既IT朋友睇下source code，確定無問題先再manual install黎用既，Github Readme度有教點manual install<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用法好簡單，你首先登入左PPS HK先，然後就按個extension既icon，會有個popup彈出黎，填好張form按執行就得喇<br />\nP.S. 第一次就淨係set行一次，試左無問題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baaZmAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaaZmAX.png&h=d42021a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果發現有咩bug既，歡迎係Github或者經Google Form話我知，Google Form條link係Github Readme度<br />\n<br />\n另外我都見到有人寫左個PPS Automator (<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/ppsautomator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fppsautomator&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=db9e237f\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/ppsautomator</a>)，咁其實佢只係公開左開頭少少關於UI(用戶介面)既code，想自己build都無得build，安唔安全就大家自行判斷啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"寫得很好，如寫多個用HSBC畀就更好"},{"pid":"e78120a69fefb378261251cc4563615e05663b5f","tid":1660642,"uid":136860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6636099b3bbd23b203b7b7492c14b1daa57121cb","tid":1660642,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5846e114e414ec13408f01f445ee